extends ./layout/layout_main.pug

block css
  style.
    .logged-in {
      display: block !important;
    }
    .logged-out {
      display: none;
    }
  //- style


block content

  .banner.home
    .gradient
    .banner-static
      img(src='assets/images/cm/banner/b2.png')
    //- banner-static
    .content
      .container
        h1.jumbo Join in the fun and save big time
          br
          small Group Buy
        //- h3
        .action
          a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg(href='#modal_signup', data-toggle='modal')
            i.fa.fa-envelope
            span.hidden-xs &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Signup with Email
          //- a
          a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg
            i.fa.fa-facebook
            span.hidden-xs &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Continue with Facebook
          //- a
        //- action
      //- container
    //- content
  //- banner-home

  section
    .container.text-center
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 What is Group Buy?
          br
          p Group Buying is the fun new way to get together with friends and save big time on your drinks, directly from the drinkmaker.
        //- col-md-12
      //- row
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 How long does a Group Buy last?
          br
          p A Group Buy closes as soon as the quantity is reached with a maximum running time of 72hrs (3 days).
        //- col-md-12
      //- row
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 How do I join a Group Buy?
          br
          p It’s really easy to do. Just find a Group Buy that looks good and join on up. You can search&nbsp;
            a(href='circlebuying.html') here.
        //- col-md-12
      //- row
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 Can I start my own Group Buy?
          br
          p You sure can it’s really simple.In just a few clicks you are on your way. Starting your own can also bring extra savings.
        //- col-md-12
      //- row
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 How do I let my friends know about my Group Buy?
          br
          p Simply share the details with your friends on the CloudMall community or with friends on other social media or email and invite them to join.
        //- col-md-12
      //- row
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 Where does my drink order go?
          br
          p Group Buying gives back the 'power to the people'.
          p By combining your orders in a Group Buy all members enjoy bulk buy rates and still get their drinks delivered directly their door.
        //- col-md-12
      //- row
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h3 Ready for lots of fun and big savings?
          br
          br
          a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg.super-action-button(href='#modal_signup', data-toggle='modal') Get Started
          | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
          a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg.super-action-button._white(href='#modal_coming_soon', data-toggle='modal') Learn more
        //- col-md-12
      //- row
    //- container
  //- section


